CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 7, 1955, pg. 12, reads: "Stunning! - This group of stunningly gowned young women were models at the fashion show given at the Fort Pitt Hotel by the Beauty Shop Owners and Beauticians of Pittsburgh during the two-day convention of state wide beauticians... - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of five women, models, including Gloria Golden Grate in center, and Gladys Harper on right, in Fort Pitt Hotel for Pittsburgh Beauty Shop Owners and Pennsylvania State Cosmetologists conference
